            "title": "Ascending the Kuai Pavilion",
            "summary": "落木千山天远大， 澄江一道月分明。 Fallen trees spread over a thousand mountains beneath a vast sky; One clear river reflects the bright moon. — Huang Tingjian 黄庭坚 (1045-1105)",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">落木千山天远大，<br>澄江一道月分明。</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Fallen trees spread over a thousand mountains beneath a vast sky;<br>One clear river reflects the bright moon.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Huang Tingjian 黄庭坚 (1045-1105)</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2893\" src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/waterfall.jpeg?w=1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/waterfall.jpeg?w=1024 1024w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/waterfall.jpeg?w=2048 2048w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/waterfall.jpeg?w=150 150w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/waterfall.jpeg?w=300 300w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/waterfall.jpeg?w=768 768w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/waterfall.jpeg?w=1440 1440w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"771\" data-attachment-id=\"2893\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/07/19/ascending-the-kuai-pavilion/waterfall/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/waterfall.jpeg\" data-orig-size=\"2800,2109\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;3aed4dd9-5e66-45ed-b121-bf8900636b2d&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Signature: &quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"waterfall\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"&lt;p&gt;Signature: &lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/waterfall.jpeg?w=960\"></figure>",
