            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/mount-zhongnan.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/mount-zhongnan.html",
            "title": "Mount Zhongnan",
            "summary": "太乙近天都， 连山接海隅。 白云回望合， 青霭入看无。 Mount Zhongnan rises toward Heaven’s capital; Its ranges stretch to the edge of the sea. Looking back, white clouds close behind; Looking in, blue mist dissolves into nothing. — Wang Wei 王维 (701-761)",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">太乙近天都，<br>连山接海隅。<br>白云回望合，<br>青霭入看无。</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Mount Zhongnan rises toward Heaven’s capital;<br>Its ranges stretch to the edge of the sea.<br>Looking back, white clouds close behind;<br>Looking in, blue mist dissolves into nothing.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Wang Wei 王维 (701-761)</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2887\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/hilly.png?w=956\" sizes=\"(max-width: 956px) 100vw, 956px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/hilly.png 956w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/hilly.png?w=150 150w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/hilly.png?w=300 300w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/hilly.png?w=768 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"956\" height=\"720\" data-attachment-id=\"2887\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/07/12/mount-zhongnan/hilly/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/hilly.png\" data-orig-size=\"956,720\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"hilly\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/hilly.png?w=956\"></figure></figure>",
