        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/lost-in-moonlight.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/lost-in-moonlight.html",
            "title": "Lost in Moonlight",
            "summary": "A warm yellow light called me, far away from behind the trees. I was in doubt, should I go? Is it a dream or am I awake? –Jacob Berghoef",
            "content_html": "<p>A warm yellow light called me, far away<br>from behind the trees. I was in doubt,<br>should I go? Is it a dream or am I awake?</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">–Jacob Berghoef</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2881\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/palm.png?w=576\" sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/palm.png 576w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/palm.png?w=113 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/palm.png?w=226 226w\" alt=\"\" width=\"576\" height=\"764\" data-attachment-id=\"2881\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/07/05/lost-in-moonlight/palm/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/palm.png\" data-orig-size=\"576,764\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"palm\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/palm.png?w=576\"></figure></figure>",
