        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/she-walks-in-beauty.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/she-walks-in-beauty.html",
            "title": "She Walks in Beauty",
            "summary": "She walks in beauty, like the night Of cloudless climes and starry skies; And all that’s best of dark and bright Meet in her aspect and her eyes… — Lord Byron",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">She walks in beauty, like the night<br>Of cloudless climes and starry skies;<br>And all that’s best of dark and bright<br>Meet in her aspect and her eyes…</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Lord Byron</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2856\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/worryfuture.png?w=648\" sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/worryfuture.png 648w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/worryfuture.png?w=113 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/worryfuture.png?w=226 226w\" alt=\"\" width=\"648\" height=\"860\" data-attachment-id=\"2856\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/06/07/she-walks-in-beauty/worryfuture/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/worryfuture.png\" data-orig-size=\"648,860\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"worryfuture\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/worryfuture.png?w=648\"></figure></figure>",
