        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/because-i-could-not-stop-for-death-.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/because-i-could-not-stop-for-death-.html",
            "title": "Because I could not stop for Death –",
            "summary": "Because I could not stop for Death – He kindly stopped for me – The Carriage held but just Ourselves – And Immortality. We slowly drove – He knew no haste And I had put away My labor and my leisure too, For His Civility&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Because I could not stop for Death –<br>He kindly stopped for me –<br>The Carriage held but just Ourselves –<br>And Immortality.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We slowly drove – He knew no haste<br>And I had put away<br>My labor and my leisure too,<br>For His Civility –</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Emily Dickinson</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2851\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/company1-copy.png?w=792\" sizes=\"(max-width: 792px) 100vw, 792px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/company1-copy.png 792w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/company1-copy.png?w=150 150w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/company1-copy.png?w=300 300w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/company1-copy.png?w=768 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"792\" height=\"792\" data-attachment-id=\"2851\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/05/31/because-i-could-not-stop-for-death/company1-copy/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/company1-copy.png\" data-orig-size=\"792,792\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"company1 copy\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/company1-copy.png?w=792\"></figure></figure>",
