        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/what-gorgeous-thing.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/what-gorgeous-thing.html",
            "title": "What Gorgeous Thing",
            "summary": "I do not know what gorgeous thing The bluebird keeps saying, His voice easing out of his throat, beak, body into the pink air of the early morning. I like it whatever it is. — Mary Oliver",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">I do not know what gorgeous thing<br>The bluebird keeps saying,<br>His voice easing out of his throat,<br>beak, body into the pink air<br>of the early morning.  I like it<br>whatever it is. </p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Mary Oliver</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2846\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/el5ur.jpg?w=771\" sizes=\"(max-width: 771px) 100vw, 771px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/el5ur.jpg?w=771 771w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/el5ur.jpg?w=1542 1542w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/el5ur.jpg?w=113 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/el5ur.jpg?w=226 226w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/el5ur.jpg?w=768 768w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/el5ur.jpg?w=1440 1440w\" alt=\"\" width=\"771\" height=\"1023\" data-attachment-id=\"2846\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/05/24/what-gorgeous-thing/el5ur/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/el5ur.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1833,2433\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"EL5uR\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/el5ur.jpg?w=771\"></figure></figure>",
            "image": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/media/posts/105/EL5uR.jpg",
