        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/jian-jia.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/jian-jia.html",
            "title": "Jian Jia",
            "summary": "蒹葭苍苍，白露为霜。 所谓伊人，在水一方。 The reeds and rushes are deeply green, The white dew has turned to frost. The one of whom I think, Is somewhere by the water’s edge. —《蒹葭》 (Jian Jia)",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">蒹葭苍苍，白露为霜。<br>所谓伊人，在水一方。</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The reeds and rushes are deeply green,<br>The white dew has turned to frost.<br>The one of whom I think,<br>Is somewhere by the water’s edge.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">—<strong>《蒹葭》 (Jian Jia)</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2840\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/loneback.png?w=720\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/loneback.png 720w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/loneback.png?w=113 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/loneback.png?w=226 226w\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"955\" data-attachment-id=\"2840\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2026/05/17/2837/loneback/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/loneback.png\" data-orig-size=\"720,955\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"loneback\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/loneback.png?w=720\"></figure></figure>",
